                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18121028-91-victim966 t18121028-91-viclabel520"></join>. What are the names of your firm - A. 
               <persName id="t18121028-91-person969">
                  Joseph 
                  Hale
               <interp inst="t18121028-91-person969" type="surname" value="Hale"></interp>
